---
description: C++ engineering rules for maintainable libraries, services, and system-level modules.
globs:
  - "**/*.cc"
  - "**/*.cpp"
  - "**/*.cxx"
  - "**/*.h"
  - "**/*.hpp"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Clarify project shape, build system, ownership model, and threading rules first.
- Prefer RAII, explicit boundaries, and testable interfaces.
- Document ownership, lifetime, and non-obvious concurrency constraints.
